{"data":{"allAboutMarkdown":{"sections":[{"frontmatter":{"imageAlt":"About me as a developer...","imageSrc":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/3aec37bc4f983876e7b8555e2575d80a/9bc57/profile-pic2.png","srcSet":"/static/3aec37bc4f983876e7b8555e2575d80a/52590/profile-pic2.png 86w,\n/static/3aec37bc4f983876e7b8555e2575d80a/a7ac7/profile-pic2.png 173w,\n/static/3aec37bc4f983876e7b8555e2575d80a/9bc57/profile-pic2.png 345w","sizes":"(min-width: 345px) 345px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/3aec37bc4f983876e7b8555e2575d80a/887aa/profile-pic2.webp 86w,\n/static/3aec37bc4f983876e7b8555e2575d80a/06d52/profile-pic2.webp 173w,\n/static/3aec37bc4f983876e7b8555e2575d80a/684ad/profile-pic2.webp 345w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 345px) 345px, 100vw"}]},"width":400,"height":463.76811594202894}}}},"html":"<p>As a developer I gained experience working with technologies ranging from Visual Basic and C# for desktop software, to PHP, JavaScript, HTML, and CSS for web applications.</p>\n<p>I honed these skills by working with frameworks like CodeIgniter, Laravel, and jQuery, developing large-scale projects in finance, inventory, sales, and accounting.</p>\n<p>I also had the opportunity to work with ERP systems such as Microsoft Dynamics SL and develop custom modules in Visual Basic.</p>\n<p>I am a self-taught developer who keeps learning constantly, always looking to improve my skills and deliver better solutions to reach team goals.</p>"}]}}}